git sconfig [<options>] [--] [<branch>...] - Configure child selection mode

    -h|--help               display help
    -0|--disable            disable child selection mode (default for submodules)
    -1|--enable             enable child selection mode
    -q|--quiet              dot not display status
    <branch>...             specific branch to enable / disable
    
example:
    git sconfig --enable            # enable child selection mode for all branches
    git sconfig --enable master     # enable child selection mode for branch 'master' only
